Introduction


Smile.G (Korean: 스마일지) was a 5-member girl group under Show Works. They consisted of: Insun, Woorin, Maxy, Lina and Jieun. They debuted on May 28, 2014 with their single “DoBiDoBob”. Unfortunately, they unofficially disbanded in December 2014.
